ome.smuggler.core.service.omero.impl

Class SessionKeepAliveHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ome.smuggler.core.service.omero.impl.SessionKeepAliveHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Reschedulable<QueuedOmeroKeepAlive>

    public class SessionKeepAliveHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements Reschedulable<QueuedOmeroKeepAlive>
    Consumes a message from the session keep-alive queue by pinging the specified OMERO session. If the ping command succeeds, a new keep-alive is scheduled; otherwise the keep-alive cycle for the given session stops.
